</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 THQ Inc., a Calabasas-based maker of video games and equipment, reported 
bigger losses in the third quarter that ended Sept. 30 as the company struggled 
to rein in costs and develop new products. 
</P>
