<P>
 Cost-cutting measures reduced selling, general and administrative expenses by 
$1.15 million in the third quarter, and the company said it has completed a 
private placement of 3.5 million shares of common stock generating proceeds of 
$1.75 million. The company said the cash will be used to market and manufacture 
a video game modem that will enable playing across telephone lines. 
