VENTURA COUNTY REVIEW: BRIEFLY: 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Jack Searles 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 October sales of new and used homes in Ventura County totaled 810, compared 
with 925 in September and 809 in October, 1993, according to Dataquick 
Information Systems. The median price last month was $186,000, down 10% from 
$208,000 a year ago. . . . Simi Valley approved a $20-million commercial 
complex to be anchored by an Iceoplex skating rink.The center, at Madera Road 
and Royal Avenue, is scheduled to open in 1996. . . . The long-troubled 
Watercourt at Westlake office complex in Westlake Village has reached 80% 
occupancy as a result of 15 new lease signings. The largest deal, worth $2.2 
million, is for 17,000 square feet to be occupied S. G. Hauser, an industrial 
design firm, reports Westcord / Westoaks Commercial Group, the center's 
marketing agent. 
