<HEADLINE>
<P>
REGIONAL ROUNDUP: MRV COMMUNICATIONS TO OFFER 1 MILLION SHARES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 MRV Communications Inc., a Chatsworth-based manufacturer of semiconductor and 
fiber optic products, said it has filed an application with the Securities and 
Exchange Commission to offer 1 million shares of common stock at $14.25 per 
share. 
</P>
<P>
 About 750,000 shares will be sold by the company and 250,000 more by certain 
stockholders. MRV said the shares could be offered next month or in January by 
an underwriting group managed by Hampshire Securities Corp. 
</P>
<P>
 The company said it would use the $9.21 million in expected net proceeds to 
fund research and development, the purchase of manufacturing and testing 
equipment, marketing activities, and possibly investment in "complementary 
businesses, products or technologies." 
</P>
