 Garamendi Seeks to End Rebate Delay: Insurance Commissioner John Garamendi 
said he asked the California Supreme Court to reverse a lower-court ruling 
delaying payment of $120 million in Proposition 103 rebates to policyholders of 
20th Century Industries. The high court on Aug. 18 rejected Woodland 
